<br>
You cannot use a  /disc to receive less damage but using a shield will by an unknown amount. <br>
<br>
You cannot have two people using the skill at the same time ( can’t shield the shielder or have two shielders on the same person ) and no one knows the re-fresh time yet.<br>
<br>
And yes you read right, mobs actually do 125% of their normal damage this way.<br>
<br>
